399
00:38:04,480 --> 00:38:06,639
[SPEAKER_01] Jer to je trajalo danima, taj nestanak struje.

400
00:38:06,639 --> 00:38:09,380
[SPEAKER_01] I to znači da nema ni kartično plaćanje, logično, ne.

401
00:38:09,380 --> 00:38:14,079
